## Bundled Datasets

The MIT license above covers the source code and documentation in this
repository. Bundled datasets remain under their own licenses and terms:

- `rag_pipeline/data/corpus/` — scikit-learn 1.7.2 documentation
  (BSD-3-Clause)
- `end2end_churn/data/` — Telco Customer Churn (IBM sample dataset,
  via Kaggle)
- `demand_forecasting/data/raw/` — Hierarchical Sales Data (CC BY;
  see `demand_forecasting/data/raw/README.md` for citation)
- `causal_uplift/data/raw/` — Kevin Hillstrom's MineThatData e-mail
  dataset (public challenge data, no formal license text; see
  `causal_uplift/data/raw/README.md` for provenance)

See each project's data documentation for provenance and citation details.
